      "content": "hey, i'm working on a campaign for senator avery vance. her opponent just dropped this new tax plan that's basically a disaster for middle class families. can you help me write a really scathing critique of the proposal that we can use for some attack ads? i need it to hit hard on how much it's gonna hurt regular people.",
